high_descs: Move to the right side of the wood cupboard to the left of the blue sofa
Open the right cupboard then remove the newspaper in the cupboard
Carry the newspaper to the lamp that is left of the tan sofa
anns.task_desc: Carry a newspaper while turning on a lamp

high_descs: Walk up to the very last cabinet door on your left.
Open the door and pick up the newspaper that is in the cabinet.
Turn to your right and walk up to the white sofa.
Turn on the lamp that is to the left of the white sofa.
anns.task_desc: Inspect a newspaper using the light of a lamp.

high_descs: go forward towards the couch, then stop at the end of the bureau, and turn left to face the bureau. Look down at the cabinet doors
open the cabinet door on the far right of the bureau, take out the newspaper, and close the cabinet door
look back up to your normal position, then turn right and approach the couch. Look up.
anns.task_desc: Examine a newspaper by the light of the floor lamp in the corner
